snippet.title: About an Elf – Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming on February 10 on the Nintendo eShop for Nintendo Switch, About an Elf is a point-and-click-ish, rpg-ish, visual-novel-ish game of elf-tastic proportions that is not be missed!

Embark on an epic adventure as you battle the mysterious King of Terrors and his army of evil monsters. Explore four fantabulous lands in search of the everlasting elftopia. Decipher the mystery of the magiballs, and employ their power to achieve total victory!
